        <hr />
        <p class="text-center">An educational website, packed with tons of interactive features to keep users engaged and educate them about the environmental issues caused by large companies around the world.</p>
        <hr />
        <div>
            <h3>Introduction</h3>
            <br />
            <p>As you have probably heard from various media outlets before, the Earth has been on a bad track for many years now, with daily carbon emissions increasing as developing countries continue to grow. This has led to Global Warming becoming an extremely prevalent issue. On this site, we have provided some reading materials, looking at how companies contribute to this issue and why we should protect the Earth!</p>
