            <div class="iframe-container">
                <iframe width="280" height="157" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wbR-5mHI6bo" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <small class="text-muted">(Video from Kurzgesagt; https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wbR-5mHI6bo&t=1s) </small>
            <br /><br />
            <div class="text-center">
                <a class="btn btn-primary text-white rounded-pill mr-2" asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Read">Learn More</a>
            </div>
            <br />
            <hr />
            <div>
                <h3>About the creators</h3>
                <br />
                <p>This informative website was developed by, Kwek Yufeng Jordan, Kai Lucas Anton, Keane Dominic Travasso, Muhammad Dandarawie Bin Rohani and Loong Chor Yi, to help bring awareness to the declining state of the environment/climate and how certain beloved companies actually contribute to this issue. The website also focuses on user interaction for engagement, as seen by the many games and inputs.</p>
                <br />
                <hr />
            </div>
            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <form target="_blank" action="https://formsubmit.co/pfdkaigrp@gmail.com" method="POST">
